moonstruck'' seemed to lure moviegoers with its nominations, but weekend receipts don't reflect an interest surge in other oscar contenders, including no. 9 ``the last emperor'' and no. 10 ``broadcast news.''
the last emperor'' got the most academy award nominations last week with nine, ``broadcast news'' got seven and ``moonstruck'' got six
