live cattle were .22 cent to .55 cent lower with april at 72.27 cents a pound; feeder cattle were .30 cent to .92 cent lower with march at 81.60 cents a pound; hogs were .17 cent to .45 cent lower with april at 43.75 cents a pound; frozen pork bellies were .40 cent to .57 cent lower with march at 53.15 cents a pound
